room_title: Escape room "Surviving Saturn" by Unchained STL in St. Louis
room_address: 221 Spencer Road Suite I Saint Peters, MO 63376
room_description:
The year is 2045 and centuries of environmental abuse have left our planet without sustainable resources. Funded by US research grants, BioChain is researching alternative energy sources in places previously left undisturbed.
Your team has been assigned to a remote collection center located in Saturn’s upper atmosphere. Your mission is to secure samples of Saturn’s gaseous emissions for testing back on earth.
